MLP AG (MLP) ,  Germany â€™s third-biggest
financial-services broker, is looking for acquisition targets,
 Boersen-Zeitung  reported, citing an interview with Chief
Financial Officer Reinhard Loose.  MLP is considering the acquisition of asset-management
companies or smaller investment-management businesses, the
